Package: CatMapR
Type: Package
Title: Interface to the CatMapper API
Version: 0.1.2
Author: Robert J. Bischoff
Maintainer: Robert J. Bischoff <bischrob@gmail.com>
Description: Provides wrappers for the CatMapper API
    <https://catmapper.org>. CatMapper organizes category systems used in
    social science and archaeology, including ethnicities, languages,
    religions, districts, and material-culture classes. The package supports
    dataset metadata discovery, category search, translation workflows, and selected
    authenticated upload operations for SocioMap and ArchaMap.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://projectcatmapper.github.io/CatMapR/,
    https://catmapper.org,
    https://github.com/ProjectCatMapper/CatMapR
BugReports: https://github.com/ProjectCatMapper/CatMapR/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
